snippet.title: MatterHackers
snippet.description:
Welcome to the MatterHackers 3D Printing Channel. Here you will find how-to tutorials, 3D printer and filament product reviews, inspiring 3D printing projects, and general shenanigans from time to time!

These videos are MatterHackers way of teaching, inspiring and empowering others to embrace the technology and make stuff using 3D printing. 

We upload new videos every week - Subscribe to get notifications through the YouTube app!

▼ To shop everything 3D printing, or to find out more information please visit our website ▼
http://www.matterhackers.com/?rcode=YTUBE
